{"tid":1064652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一輩子嘅情人？相逢恨晚？","createTime":"2019-03-16T17:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T02:24:22.000Z","uid":212487,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9ead84e6cb099d36c5af07630b294de716b6ac","tid":1064652,"uid":212487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"分手後同一個一直感情幾好嘅男仔行埋咗<br />\n佢一直睇住我同男朋友嘅問題 一直到分手嗰日<br />\n係佢陪我渡過最難捱嘅時刻<br />\n但佢有另一半<br />\n我一刻都冇諗過要霸住佢甚至要求任何名份<br />\n但佢比到我拍拖都從來都冇嘅安全感同埋愛惜 大家唔洗講野都知道對方諗乜野<br />\n我知道依段感情唔會有結果 我只係想珍惜一個同樣珍惜自己嘅人<br />\n但我多多少少都有因為佢嘅身分糾結過<br />\n點解愛一個人會係咁奮不顧身？"},{"pid":"1d32a16dcdefc7909a6cd846da982e674d36a2c1","tid":1064652,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:49:17.000Z","msg":"Me lazy no read"},{"pid":"56cb66f74b550aecdb14b5d57cf1ac949dd61ec5","tid":1064652,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"我忍唔住...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a71c3fd7795fbde1961990ecd140e6cc3bebf6e","tid":1064652,"uid":203774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:51:13.000Z","msg":"is bitch didn't read"},{"pid":"75d333ab0927e80570969ce5f9cfe24204cb2297","tid":1064652,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56cb66f74b550aecdb14b5d57cf1ac949dd61ec5","tid":1064652,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"我忍唔住...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"望到標題忍唔咗..."},{"pid":"226252cdbaa969eb746e6db0d7d888accd0f10ec","tid":1064652,"uid":74162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"分分鐘破壞到人地感情就好自私囉"},{"pid":"e01da8fa807584dfb9f7538d92c587e2c7f543ae","tid":1064652,"uid":46480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"拍左感覺就會唔同"},{"pid":